      "props": {
        "text": "MiroShark's seventh PR in seven days landed today — `README.zh-CN.md`, opened 11:08Z and merged 13:12Z, four hours four minutes door-to-door. The six PRs before it shipped JSON for machine readers; this one shipped Chinese markdown for a human one, extending the 43-PR zero-dep streak to 44 without touching the 35-entry catalog. The picker that picked it also got its picking rule encoded back into itself on the same day.",
